# Flutter Client Conventions

See [MASTER_BLUEPRINT.md](../../MASTER_BLUEPRINT.md) § Flutter Mobile Client.

- State: Riverpod providers in `lib/core/di.dart`
- HTTP: Dio with JWT interceptor; base URL from `AppConstants.baseUrl` (dev gateway :8080)
- Offline: Hive for GPS waypoints; sync via `SyncService` on activity save
- Background GPS: `flutter_background_service` + `geolocator` stream → Hive
- Maps: `flutter_map` + OpenStreetMap tiles; render routes from GeoJSON
- Navigation: GoRouter with auth guard
